" packer
augroup vim.packer.fmt
  autocmd!
  autocmd BufWritePost *.pkr.hcl silent! !packer fmt <afile>
  autocmd BufWritePost * edit
  autocmd BufWritePost * redraw!
augroup END

" Test
nmap <silent> <leader>t :TestNearest<CR>
nmap <silent> <leader>T :TestFile<CR>
